com.ac.games.rest.controller

Class GameReltnController

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ac.games.rest.controller.GameReltnController

  • @RestController
@RequestMapping(value="/gamereltn")
public class GameReltnController
extends Object
    This class should be the intercepter for REST service access to the core Game information.

    It should handle all request that come in under the /gamereltn entry.

    Refer to the individual methods to determine the parameter lists.
